{"id": 565, "genre": 1000, "title": "中国的时尚设计，你有啥想说的？", "description": "啊！高冷！酷炫！不知道咋买！不知道咋穿！不知道咋搭配！（题图来自Peter Oumanski）", "record_count": 5807, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194624my2qLaC95gOxzk41.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-13T01:09:10Z", "questions": [{"id": 466, "title": "中国的时尚设计，你有啥想说的？", "content": "中国的时尚设计，你有啥想说的？\r\n", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 15917, "content": "特别想见识，但根本不知道哪里卖", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193348Kvs3RI0l5u8FG47a.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 15918, "content": "这么贵，你们想过同样价钱能买什么吗", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193945PgKyTNn8jr3fGID4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 15919, "content": "样式夸张，除了模特本人之外咋穿咋丑", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193348Q5KaBXZuhvxbVDFt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 15921, "content": "我也想支持中国设计，但……有我能穿的款吗", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193348W3xBgXL1IedwFSU4.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 15922, "content": "花了这么多钱想买百搭款，但结果多半是白搭款", "image": "img/option/option/201606071933487oXknzFiIHq31OYt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 15923, "content": "都没什么明星设计师，让我不知怎么往外炫耀", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193349xR34qUAdHBu5MDYX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 15924, "content": "无论如何，我有点怕中国风的设计", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193350whQlbTJLCdYg27qn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 15925, "content": "什么隐喻？什么游走在时尚文化中的谄媚与批判之间？", "image": "img/option/option/201606071933502QE6pahsjrf47YU5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}